contact www.OpenSubtitles.org today

03:29.845 --> 03:31.445
♪

03:37.619 --> 03:39.219
♪

03:45.092 --> 03:47.460
♪ And at the break of day ♪

03:47.529 --> 03:52.198
♪ you sank into your dream ♪

03:52.266 --> 03:53.399
♪ you dreamer ♪

03:53.466 --> 03:56.268
♪ oh, oh, oh... ♪

03:56.336 --> 03:58.270
♪ you dreamer ♪

